{"tid":513463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而舉黃色標語人士將「Joy to the world」填上新歌詞，變成「拉朱經緯」！","createTime":"2017-12-29T14:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T16:09:17.000Z","uid":5812,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"badb3e04b383b26e25b37396a39d5475edf6974c","tid":513463,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:13:25.000Z","msg":"【17：10】<br />\n載著朱經緯的囚車離開法院，前往茘枝角收押所，在法院大樓囚車出口位置，兩旁分別排列著撐警大聯盟及舉黃色標語、支持將朱經緯繩之於法的人，雙方互叫「收黑錢，死全家」。而舉黃色標語人士將「Joy to the world」填上新歌詞，變成「拉朱經緯」，並在囚車出口位置大聲播放。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「拉朱經緯」「拉朱經緯」拉朱經緯，經緯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ffacd986e4248093a0069f0191157a1ba9feee4","tid":513463,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:15:00.000Z","msg":"有無巴打有片，想聽歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eedbef3e7db0f77b0314b7586ab0fb721284f764","tid":513463,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa05c4b90c1812461719788b22c56acf568a14a8","tid":513463,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8229928b244aff7686944b3afc6dabec1b7ec77","tid":513463,"uid":26506,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:20:25.000Z","msg":"&quot; <br />\n乜鬼都買　好鬼高興<br />\nChristmas shopping shopping<br />\n一九九七一早注定　新衫新錶應早買定<br />\n莫待日後賣清　到時頭暈頭㷫<br />\n買件油多都要話睇身份證<br />\n<br />\n今天不買　他朝盞慶　Shouting<br />\n小平　小平<br />\n因此今天不必冷靜　沙煲罌罉一早買定<br />\n莫待日後賣清　到時頭暈頭慶<br />\n買盒牙簽都要話擔心呃枰<br />\n&quot; <br />\n-- (1989)"},{"pid":"61f999eec0f8afbb4b7fc6f7dacdd62eb4b59951","tid":513463,"uid":82354,"l